title: WWE Superstar Xavier Woods Is Hosting Kinda Funny Live 3!
description:
Get your ticket now at http://www.kindafunny.com/kfl3

Kinda Funny Live 3 is June 3rd in San Francisco, CA at The Regency Ballroom.

Check out last year's show here: https://youtu.be/6l6IHWmvlHE

transcript_chunks.text: It's a new day, yes it is. Cetera live is so close and it's about to be so damn cool. A lot of people have been asking who is going to host the show this year KFL 1 we had the illustrious Troy Baker, KFL 2 we had Rooster Teeth's Burnie Burns, and ladies and gentlemen I'm proud to officially announce that WWE Superstar Xavier Woods will be hosting Kinda Funny Live three. It's a new day indeed. Also making a return KFL appearance is Mega64, who is once again going to tear the house down. Of course there's a ton more surprise guests but you know all right let's talk about the three limited exclusive posters first off here is the amazing official KFL 3 poster designed by Panda Musk. Obviously I'm a big fan of this one. Next up we got a fun one designed by Bab Star, the artist behind The Boondocks. So hell yeah. yeah finally the man the myth the legend Cool Greg designed this one and got it digitized by fellow best friend Travis Smith and that's pretty damn cool now moving on to t-shirts we have two limited edition exclusive shirts designed by Andy Cortez that are Super Rad first off we have this year's official KFL 3 tour shirt and check out the hotness that is the KFL 3 Mech shirt damn we are also debuting two new shirts that aren't exclusive to kind of funny live one is a surprise and the other is the collection shirt where we crowdsourced fake game names from you and man I love that teal thank you anyways it is officially Time to Get Hype you can get your ticket now at kindofunny.com/kfl3 and I cannot wait to see you all there make sure you check out the forums to stay up to date on all the community events going on all weekend it's going to be awesome until next time let's go host
